import React from 'react'; import '../../assets/style/FlightRecord.css'; const FlightRecord = ({ location, destination, departure, airline, duration, arrival, price, travelType }) => { return (

Location

{location}

{destination}

Departure

Date: {departure.date}

Time: {departure.time}

Airport: {departure.airport}

Airline

{airline}

Duration

{duration}

Arrival

Date: {arrival.date}

Time: {arrival.time}

Airport: {arrival.airport}

Price: {price}

Travel Type: {travelType}

); }; export default FlightRecord;
